      "title": "A JOINT RESOLUTION requesting Congress recognize the protection of Wyoming's freedom of access to public lands, to allow responsible development of resources, recreation, agriculture, hunting, fishing, trapping, and conservation under multiple\u2011use frameworks, to protect local participation in land management decisions, and to keep public lands available to the people of Wyoming."
    }
  ],
